  "Description": {
    "English": "A specialist <span class=\"name name-stellar\">bait</span> for <span class=\"name name-fuel\">carnivores</span>. Use the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span> to discover the bait preferences of specific creatures.<br><br>Created in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Nutrient Processor</span> from <span class=\"name name-special\">Mordite</span> and assorted <span class=\"name name-fuel\">creature flesh</span>.<br><br>Feeding using the correct bait will allow creatures to be <VAL_ON>ridden<> or <VAL_ON>harvested<>. It will also <VAL_ON>calm predators<>. Chose bait type from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种专业<span class=\"name name-stellar\">诱饵</span>，适用于<span class=\"name name-fuel\">食肉动物</span>。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>发现特定生物的诱饵偏好。<br><br>用<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>制造，材料是<span class=\"name name-special\">腐藤</span>和各种<span class=\"name name-fuel\">生物肉</span>。<br><br>使用正确的诱饵喂食后，可<VAL_ON>骑乘<>或<VAL_ON>收取<>动物。同时可<VAL_ON>安抚捕食者<>。从快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）中选择诱饵类型。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种专业<span class=\"name name-stellar\">诱饵</span>，适用于<span class=\"name name-fuel\">食肉动物</span>。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>发现特定生物的诱饵偏好。<br><br>用<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>制造，材料是<span class=\"name name-special\">腐藤</span>和各种<span class=\"name name-fuel\">生物肉</span>。<br><br>使用正确的诱饵喂食后，可<VAL_ON>骑乘<>或<VAL_ON>收取<>动物。同时可<VAL_ON>安抚捕食者<>。从快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）中选择诱饵类型。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "專門的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">誘餌</span>，專為<span class=\"name name-fuel\">肉食生物</span>所用。利用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>即可了解特定生物偏好哪一種誘餌。<br><br>利用<span class=\"name name-technology\">營養處理器</span>製造，原料是<span class=\"name name-special\">歿鹽</span>與各種<span class=\"name name-fuel\">生物肉</span>。<br><br>餵食正確的誘餌，即可<VAL_ON>騎乘<>或<VAL_ON>採收<>生物，誘餌也可以讓<VAL_ON>獵食性生物<>平靜下來。利用快捷選單（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）可選擇誘餌種類。"
  },
